Port_Orange.Delos A. Blodgett House:
The Delos A. Blodgett House (also known as 8VO4385) is a historic house located at 404 Ridgewood Avenue in Daytona Beach, Florida.


== Description and history ==
The 2-1/2 story Queen Anne style house was completed in 1896 for Delos A. Blodgett and his wife Daisy A. Peck. It was listed on the National Register of Historic Places on August 2, 1993.
